  "detailed_description": "<h1>Add to your wishlist!</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326020/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.poster.avif?t=1689378603\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326020/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.webm?t=1689378603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326020/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.mp4?t=1689378603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><h1>You may also like</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><strong>To progress through each level, the player must possess specific essential items that are necessary for its completion.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326020/extras/2233420904a3cc7b9184ffaa3159a758.avif?t=1689378603\" width=500 height=410 /></span><br><strong>In order to obtain these items, you must meticulously arrange your items and  treasures within your inventory.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326020/extras/6a2b53e5d2d26189727e33dc6b699cb1.poster.avif?t=1689378603\" width=500 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326020/extras/6a2b53e5d2d26189727e33dc6b699cb1.webm?t=1689378603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326020/extras/6a2b53e5d2d26189727e33dc6b699cb1.mp4?t=1689378603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>After that you'll need to engage in the process of selling your treasures to the merchant.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326020/extras/bcf42a031af9e6416bd6972dd29c012e.poster.avif?t=1689378603\" width=502 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326020/extras/bcf42a031af9e6416bd6972dd29c012e.webm?t=1689378603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326020/extras/bcf42a031af9e6416bd6972dd29c012e.mp4?t=1689378603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Now, armed with a substantial amount of pesetas, you possess the means to procure the items you require!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326020/extras/62be3979c66a2d66887247c0b02aebd6.poster.avif?t=1689378603\" width=502 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326020/extras/62be3979c66a2d66887247c0b02aebd6.webm?t=1689378603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326020/extras/62be3979c66a2d66887247c0b02aebd6.mp4?t=1689378603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>To successfully complete the level, all that remains is to place the purchased items back into your inventory.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326020/extras/b53d744688c9846444e6faf9ba978e45.poster.avif?t=1689378603\" width=500 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326020/extras/b53d744688c9846444e6faf9ba978e45.webm?t=1689378603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326020/extras/b53d744688c9846444e6faf9ba978e45.mp4?t=1689378603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><strong>Use your organizing skills to make all your items fit. </strong></strong><br></li><li><strong>Use your logical thinking to balance your finances and be able to buy the items needed.</strong><br></li><li><strong>Understand the format of several items to find the best fitting.</strong><br></li><li><strong>40 unique handmade levels.</strong><br></li><li><strong>Relaxing music and sound effects made for the game!    </strong></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><strong>To progress through each level, the player must possess specific essential items that are necessary for its completion.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326020/extras/2233420904a3cc7b9184ffaa3159a758.avif?t=1689378603\" width=500 height=410 /></span><br><strong>In order to obtain these items, you must meticulously arrange your items and  treasures within your inventory.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326020/extras/6a2b53e5d2d26189727e33dc6b699cb1.poster.avif?t=1689378603\" width=500 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326020/extras/6a2b53e5d2d26189727e33dc6b699cb1.webm?t=1689378603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326020/extras/6a2b53e5d2d26189727e33dc6b699cb1.mp4?t=1689378603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>After that you'll need to engage in the process of selling your treasures to the merchant.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326020/extras/bcf42a031af9e6416bd6972dd29c012e.poster.avif?t=1689378603\" width=502 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326020/extras/bcf42a031af9e6416bd6972dd29c012e.webm?t=1689378603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326020/extras/bcf42a031af9e6416bd6972dd29c012e.mp4?t=1689378603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Now, armed with a substantial amount of pesetas, you possess the means to procure the items you require!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326020/extras/62be3979c66a2d66887247c0b02aebd6.poster.avif?t=1689378603\" width=502 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326020/extras/62be3979c66a2d66887247c0b02aebd6.webm?t=1689378603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326020/extras/62be3979c66a2d66887247c0b02aebd6.mp4?t=1689378603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>To successfully complete the level, all that remains is to place the purchased items back into your inventory.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326020/extras/b53d744688c9846444e6faf9ba978e45.poster.avif?t=1689378603\" width=500 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326020/extras/b53d744688c9846444e6faf9ba978e45.webm?t=1689378603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326020/extras/b53d744688c9846444e6faf9ba978e45.mp4?t=1689378603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><strong>Use your organizing skills to make all your items fit. </strong></strong><br></li><li><strong>Use your logical thinking to balance your finances and be able to buy the items needed.</strong><br></li><li><strong>Understand the format of several items to find the best fitting.</strong><br></li><li><strong>40 unique handmade levels.</strong><br></li><li><strong>Relaxing music and sound effects made for the game!    </strong></li></ul>",
